{"tid":2009484,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個人對自己好失望","createTime":"2020-05-09T18:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T06:04:35.000Z","uid":310593,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34b4db7f01530fbbdf6e3ac9afb631e893ab2b37","tid":2009484,"uid":310593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:27:06.000Z","msg":"琴日女朋友鬧交，跟著今日成日冇講野，頭先佢send左句 &rdquo;我對你愈黎愈失望&rdquo;黎。。個心即刻勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n痛嘅係因為原來自己不知不覺中成為左自己最憎嘅個種人，嗰啲講一套做一套嘅人。同埋我究竟傷害到佢成點，佢先會講得出呢句野。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢啲人都係自己一個人算，唔好出黎害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b5eb7421fc553d542593999fd90dcb6b0130de","tid":2009484,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:27:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cc70894771ab690a6e1a84b45a4804bbfe8fa4f","tid":2009484,"uid":193474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:28:51.000Z","msg":"咁要睇吓你做咗啲咩先<br />\n佢講出口 一係你真係好過份 一係佢冇諗你感受"},{"pid":"9b56acc177b9ea45092679e32a0542ba2b434820","tid":2009484,"uid":203701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:42:33.000Z","msg":"趁重有得救 改啦"},{"pid":"7fecae23292f2184afc092caeb9c3619fd26935b","tid":2009484,"uid":253461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:51:45.000Z","msg":"你仲識得痛 都叫做自己知咩事啦 唔好等到個女仔心淡個陣先黎後悔 到時真係冇人幫到你"},{"pid":"ab83f69172c6266eea0fadf8632fd1c0068cedfa","tid":2009484,"uid":310593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:20:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得今次好返，都仲會有下次，咁樣只會繼續傷害佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8b60219f92fe99c457c3837892aaf55052ff54",